{"tid":217842,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"打救地盤新手","createTime":"2017-04-26T05:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T17:22:10.000Z","uid":97903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4e18d3d6c1432e997cf2fd20b41acdcd399b0c","tid":217842,"uid":97903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"得知連登好多都係地盤既師父/師兄<br />\n<br />\n小弟5月開始番工，聽聞跟朋友做水喉<br />\n<br />\n想問下通常新手入去做要咩條件，或許要帶d咩開工？<br />\n<br />\n因為小弟本身都幾大汗 想睇下有咩方法應付<br />\n<br />\n同埋地盤佬係咪個個都屌哂老母咁？不過小弟本身都襟屌，唔係問題既<br />\n<br />\n仲有有無登連地盤師父比d咩建意我依個新手 等我可以應對<br />\n麻煩哂咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5eda3ccbdeed9da43c6c17e16b8e77c6ad3cb6c","tid":217842,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:54:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得知連登好多都係地盤既師父/師兄<br />\n<br />\n小弟5月開始番工，聽聞跟朋友做水喉<br />\n<br />\n想問下通常新手入去做要咩條件，或許要帶d咩開工？<br />\n<br />\n因為小弟本身都幾大汗 想睇下有咩方法應付<br />\n<br />\n同埋地盤佬係咪個個都屌哂老母咁？不過小弟本身都襟屌，唔係問題既<br />\n<br />\n仲有有無登連地盤師父比d咩建意我依個新手 等我可以應對<br />\n麻煩哂咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你係女咪唔會屌囉(熟咗另計)"},{"pid":"0d3f91e3aedcfe0d8a1cd0ba21f6513611d6ce26","tid":217842,"uid":97903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>得知連登好多都係地盤既師父/師兄<br />\n<br />\n小弟5月開始番工，聽聞跟朋友做水喉<br />\n<br />\n想問下通常新手入去做要咩條件，或許要帶d咩開工？<br />\n<br />\n因為小弟本身都幾大汗 想睇下有咩方法應付<br />\n<br />\n同埋地盤佬係咪個個都屌哂老母咁？不過小弟本身都襟屌，唔係問題既<br />\n<br />\n仲有有無登連地盤師父比d咩建意我依個新手 等我可以應對<br />\n麻煩哂咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你係女咪唔會屌囉(熟咗另計)</blockquote><br />\n可惜我係男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5bae7f5bb4ed18950d8f3a93d0e1c8e9e92664","tid":217842,"uid":38352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:00:17.000Z","msg":"要人教你晏就食飯要識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436a7d4638dd1e4b6fbcd1dcee777543a7e4bec4","tid":217842,"uid":97903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:39:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要人教你晏就食飯要識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依樣我識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4893b16813c1e62be82df16cfbe9c6d9d5ad70","tid":217842,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"帶煙"},{"pid":"7f5c1a4de2e7a9fe1e57aed36fba6e0e92db4622","tid":217842,"uid":66877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"無野要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實地盤佬好有禮貌，唔同行頭都尊重對方<br />\n師兄前師兄後，屌哂老母果d通常自己熟果班<br />\n<br />\n要注意既咪安全，大量爆左既卡板，爛棚竹，不同類型既陷阱在地下or棚架，小心行就得。<br />\n仲有出棚做野記得帶帽，真係有用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49f27dae475271baf294d1e239c00b7f4ae6794","tid":217842,"uid":89449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:29:21.000Z","msg":"返過一日  原來d地盤佬好好禮貌仲好好吹，<br />\n<br />\n所以唔洗驚比人屌"},{"pid":"963ec10942ad0daead076d2abeb8017a405138ba","tid":217842,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返過一日  原來d地盤佬好好禮貌仲好好吹，<br />\n<br />\n所以唔洗驚比人屌</blockquote><br />\n你唔搞到佢咪冇事囉"},{"pid":"ba11ba8f559f6d756824adde802d5f8756c35b6b","tid":217842,"uid":97903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:10:50.000Z","msg":"咁其實要帶對安全鞋去換 定著住去？"},{"pid":"46a9f438f666133af4a24a3c9ea95da8aed912b4","tid":217842,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁其實要帶對安全鞋去換 定著住去？</blockquote><br />\n由得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我自己就帶左對放係嗰到返去換"},{"pid":"9719b57a39bd9a2ed2b9198144a2536645d1f758","tid":217842,"uid":97903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"各位巴打 做地盤容唔容易瘦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d959b96d158be9c18744cb24a75621903250afdd","tid":217842,"uid":36754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"買定工具，安全鞋先啦"},{"pid":"237d168663f106620276a3e67b8b4b5a9d49665c","tid":217842,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:37:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位巴打 做地盤容唔容易瘦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開頭做左第一個月瘦左兩kg同曬黑晒,又日日無精神咁返屋企"},{"pid":"485e329ae0187f8efe5934aee708e65ff464ad71","tid":217842,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返過一日  原來d地盤佬好好禮貌仲好好吹，<br />\n<br />\n所以唔洗驚比人屌</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6bca921d120756547a3cd94e139c5673c9ed40f7","tid":217842,"uid":24453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:41:45.000Z","msg":"買包煙仔🚬🐋"},{"pid":"61ce6210814f9f4e8028cb61a83b71ba884f8895","tid":217842,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:42:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返過一日  原來d地盤佬好好禮貌仲好好吹，<br />\n<br />\n所以唔洗驚比人屌</blockquote><br />\n你就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我以前跟嗰個乜鳩都屌 <br />\n其他師博教我地野又比佢屌，做安全措施又比佢屌，有個師兄見佢推重野唔夠力就跌去幫一幫人又比佢屌，佢自己又唔係點教我地野，借人工具就問都唔問拎左人啲野用，人地問佢借就屌人老母唔撚借咁，最後佢得罪晒地罪啲人，所以跟完佢之後我都無做lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605ba3603b6602d46baf683f17a066bfc612f69d","tid":217842,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>返過一日  原來d地盤佬好好禮貌仲好好吹，<br />\n<br />\n所以唔洗驚比人屌</blockquote><br />\n你就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我以前跟嗰個乜鳩都屌 <br />\n其他師博教我地野又比佢屌，做安全措施又比佢屌，有個師兄見人地推重野唔夠力就跌去幫一幫人又比佢屌，佢自己又唔係點教我地野，借人工具就問都唔問拎左人啲野用，人地問佢借就屌人老母唔撚借咁，最後佢得罪晒地罪啲人，所以跟完佢之後我都無做lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"64eca71bc5c200e75f1d0176c81e7795ef24c5da","tid":217842,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:43:49.000Z","msg":"叫雞賭馬食煙飲酒呢d係基本啦，如果唔係好難埋到堆。<br />\n仲要識得地盤禮儀，習慣每句開頭都要講&quot;屌~~~你老尾&quot;，坐巴士就算識都要隔開幾行坐。"},{"pid":"04aa51d01c0755999804c4a26e87cc8c44db3c94","tid":217842,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:49:01.000Z","msg":"注意安全就得<br />\n唔撚好急"},{"pid":"b678744c6c38e6df582ae00c0a10615d7f7d6535","tid":217842,"uid":97903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:15:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫雞賭馬食煙飲酒呢d係基本啦，如果唔係好難埋到堆。<br />\n仲要識得地盤禮儀，習慣每句開頭都要講&quot;屌~~~你老尾&quot;，坐巴士就算識都要隔開幾行坐。</blockquote><br />\n我有家室 唔賭唔飲酒 岩岩戒左煙<br />\n咁咪埋唔到佢地堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16802f2ef6b3d95a785d1dcbea72d5c94cfe5afe","tid":217842,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:21:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫雞賭馬食煙飲酒呢d係基本啦，如果唔係好難埋到堆。<br />\n仲要識得地盤禮儀，習慣每句開頭都要講&quot;屌~~~你老尾&quot;，坐巴士就算識都要隔開幾行坐。</blockquote><br />\n我有家室 唔賭唔飲酒 岩岩戒左煙<br />\n咁咪埋唔到佢地堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都係去考ACO算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de852486d80c3c40ad738f33bf8d53f36430ae9","tid":217842,"uid":40422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:25:08.000Z","msg":"望多d 記多d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e964e116b9ae558eba440683d4afced00ec089c","tid":217842,"uid":97903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>望多d 記多d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfea343ab9a47491473f69217b39a7a3b32bb0f4","tid":217842,"uid":25340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:41:43.000Z","msg":"屌唔屌好睇師傅<br />\n不過時代唔同 我見好多師傅屌都唔會屌得勁<br />\n想埋推最好就食煙啦 得閒請下師傅食<br />\n唔食的話就勤力d做多d記多d<br />\n咩都爭住做 佢地都唔會對你差<br />\n最緊要係學識謙卑<br />\n就算學過記得都聽佢地意見"},{"pid":"5a138ffe5f2c6081c4e6c7134d85b1d24e307186","tid":217842,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>望多d 記多d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做多d 練多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽多d 主動d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問多d 勤力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學多d 醒目d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae655a51af5e9a4eeea101ad3d3cb2cf6668478e","tid":217842,"uid":97903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:35:59.000Z","msg":"如果咁熱既天氣 你地有咩應對方法？"},{"pid":"79709a7c407ba3a3d527261b1930803728ad7fdb","tid":217842,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果咁熱既天氣 你地有咩應對方法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔熱先返工<br />\n其他射波"},{"pid":"a77d997bdf76c23cd439e89c17baa2d45c179454","tid":217842,"uid":97903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T12:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果咁熱既天氣 你地有咩應對方法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔熱先返工<br />\n其他射波</blockquote><br />\n咁又唔得 要養家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0485eee2923ad1ee3b4f4deb1dc88f50ca5d7b0b","tid":217842,"uid":97903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T06:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05468c9733edb9235a23854b6e91affc01eb9e8f","tid":217842,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫雞賭馬食煙飲酒呢d係基本啦，如果唔係好難埋到堆。<br />\n仲要識得地盤禮儀，習慣每句開頭都要講&quot;屌~~~你老尾&quot;，坐巴士就算識都要隔開幾行坐。</blockquote><br />\n我有家室 唔賭唔飲酒 岩岩戒左煙<br />\n咁咪埋唔到佢地堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常無做過地盤既人, 先會以為地盤佬都係 食煙叫雞<br />\n你要食煙叫雞, 先可以埋到堆<br />\n<br />\n事實上, 唔係每個地盤佬都會食煙叫雞<br />\n而且你埋唔埋到堆, 同你有冇食煙叫雞 無關係, 主要睇你個人性格係點<br />\n<br />\n你性格隨和, 就可以埋堆<br />\n你性格衰, 就神僧鬼厭<br />\n<br />\n我一樣唔食煙, 唔叫雞........但我做左地盤六年, 一樣同D師傅關係良好"},{"pid":"d43b3e3a03b7e7dc754d13245167331740bb83d1","tid":217842,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T23:32:41.000Z","msg":"巴打返工返成點呀？"},{"pid":"4520328a6f94eeaca5491560858a4a145abc4db5","tid":217842,"uid":88495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T05:05:34.000Z","msg":"爸打果到仲請唔請人？我都想返地盤啊"},{"pid":"b48c55006aa6afbfa47b07561c13e85d24afd397","tid":217842,"uid":85431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:19:33.000Z","msg":"有冇人指教下新入行磚仔佬詳細係點做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005cc69b2cf584489d0c57b539a5c2f91e7385fe","tid":217842,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:21:37.000Z","msg":"